Class Librarian

  • java.lang.Object
    • Librarian

  • public class Librarian
extends java.lang.Object
    Librarian.java
    Since:
    19/11/2018
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Zak Chambers Hale & Alex Jones Subclass of Account that has administrative privileges on the system for procedures such as adding resources and users among others, that normal users cannot access. Librarians hold extra information to normal users(staff number and employment date).
